OL,3,CNottingham hospital staff sent emails
OL,4,Cabout families whose babies died
OL,6,FSenior members of staff at Nottingham
OL,7,Fhospitals sent "horrible" emails about
OL,8,Ffamilies whose babies had died in
OL,9,Ftheir care, a review has found.
OL,11,FNottingham University Hospitals (NUH)
OL,12,Fis subject to the largest maternity
OL,13,Freview in NHS history following
OL,14,Fhundreds of baby deaths and injuries,
OL,15,Fwith almost 2,000 families' cases
OL,16,Fbeing included.
