OL,6,FReview chair, experienced midwife
OL,7,FDonna Ockenden, said internal
OL,8,Fcorrespondence between some employees
OL,9,Facross the Queen's Medical Centre and
OL,10,FCity Hospital included "derogatory,
OL,11,Funkind and insensitive" comments
OL,12,Ftowards families.
OL,14,FShe described the behaviour as
OL,15,F"absolutely unacceptable" and the
OL,16,Femails as "horrible".
OL,18,FNUH apologised "unreservedly" to
OL,19,Fanyone affected and said offenders
OL,20,Fwould be "properly dealt with" in line
OL,21,Fwith its HR rules.
