OL,6,FThey said people within the trust were
OL,7,F"victim-blaming" and more concerned
OL,8,Fabout the reputation of staff.
OL,10,FIn an email on October 4, 2017, a
OL,11,Fsenior staff member accused the pair
OL,12,Fof lying in a press release through
OL,13,Fsolicitors.
OL,15,FThey wrote: "Is there anything at all
OL,16,Fthat can be done about the lies?"
OL,18,FThe same staff member said they were
OL,19,Fdefaming individuals at the hospital
OL,20,Fand sent in another email: "This press
OL,21,Frelease is full of untruths.
